20I%20started%20drinking%20heavily%20to%20cope%20with%20the%20stress%20and%20help%20myself%20fall%20asleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20able%20to%20function%20while%20drinking%20one%20or%20two%20bottles%20of%20wine%20before%20bed%2C%20but%20I%20started%20ignoring%20my%20own%20personal%20policies%20on%20drinking%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0like%20not%20drinking%20on%20planes%20and%20while%20traveling.%20Suddenly%2C%20I%20was%20drinking%20in%20airports%2C%20on%20planes%2C%20and%20at%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20trying%20to%20numb%20the%20painful%20truth%20of%20my%20own%20unhappiness%20while%20pretending%20to%20the%20outside%20world%20that%20I%20had%20it%20all%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2294f2193b-83c5-4faf-abf6-83179723ea73%5C%22%3ESeeking%20help%20made%20me%20confront%20my%20unhappiness%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decline%20in%20my%20physical%20well-being%2C%20which%20included%20weight%20gain%2C%20stomach%20issues%2C%20chronic%20coughing%2C%20and%20overall%20feelings%20of%20exhaustion%2C%20forced%20me%20to%20see%20a%20doctor%20in%20early%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20see%20a%20doctor%20who%20specialized%20in%20Eastern%20and%20Western%20medicine%20so%20I%20could%20share%20that%20what%20I%20was%20experiencing%20was%20mental%2C%20physical%2C%20emotional%2C%20and%20spiritual.%20Sharing%20and%20accepting%20that%20I%20was%20unhappy%20was%20how%20I%20started%20on%20the%20path%20to%20leaving%20the%20corporate%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20quit%20Harley%20Davidson%20in%20September%202016%2C%20and%20I%20stopped%20having%20nightmares.%20I%20worked%20with%20my%20financial%20advisor%2C%20and%20while%20I%20wasn't%20in%20a%20position%20to%20retire%2C%20I%20did%20have%20enough%20savings%20to%20give%20me%20some%20leeway%20while%20I%20decided%20on%20my%20next%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20I%20didn't%20know%20what%20to%20do%20next%2C%20but%20I've%20since%20found%20my%20calling%20in%20helping%20others%20define%20their%20own%20version%20of%20success%20%E2%80