n%20options%2C%20including%20credit%20cards%20and%20personal%20loans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhen%20Will%20House%20Prices%20Come%20Down%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20aren't%20likely%20to%20see%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhome-prices-drop%5C%22%3Ehome%20prices%20drop%3C%2Fa%3E%20anytime%20soon%20thanks%20to%20extremely%20limited%20supply.%20In%20fact%2C%20they'll%20likely%20rise%20this%20year%20as%20mortgage%20rates%20drop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fanniemae.com%2Fmedia%2F51391%2Fdisplay%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFannie%20Mae%20researchers%3C%2Fa%3E%20expect%20prices%20to%20increase%204.8%25%20in%202024%2C%20while%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mba.org%2Fnews-and-research%2Fforecasts-and-commentary%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMortgage%20Bankers%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%20expects%20a%204.3%25%20increase%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELower%20mortgage%20rates%20will%20bring%20more%20buyers%20onto%20the%20market%2C%20putting%20upward%20pressure%20on%20prices.%20But%20prices%20aren't%20currently%20expected%20to%20increase%20as%20much%20as%20they%20have%20in%20recent%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFixed-Rate%20vs.%20Adjustable-Rate%20Mortgage%20Pros%20and%20Cons%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-fixed-rate-mortgage%5C%22%3EFixed-rate%20mortgages%3C%2Fa%3E%20lock%20in%20your%20rate%20for%20the%20entire%20life%20of%20your%20loan.%20Adjustable-rate%20mortgages%20lock%20in%20your%20rate%20for%20the%20first%20few%20years%2C%20then%20your%20rate%20goes%20up%20or%20down%20periodically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20how%20do%20you%20choose%20between%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ffixed-rate-mortgage-vs-adjustable-rate-mortgage%5C%22%3Efixed-rate%20vs.%20adjustable-rate%20mortgage%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EARMs%20typically%20start%20with%20lower%20rates%20than%20fixed-rate%20mortgages%2C%20but%20ARM%20rates%20can%20go%20up%20once%20your%20initial%20introductory%20period%20is%20over.%20If%20you%20plan%20on%20moving%20or%20refinancing%20before%20the%20rate%20adjusts%2C%20an%20ARM%20could%20be%20a%20good%20deal.%20But%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20a%20change%20in%20circumstances%20could%20prevent%20you%20from%20doing%20these%20things%2C%20so%20it's%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20think%20about%20whether%20your%20budget%20could%20handle%20a%20higher%20monthly%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFixed-rate%20mortgage%20are%20a%20good%20choice%20for%20borrowers%20who%20want%20stability%2C%20since%20your%20monthly%20principal%20and%20interest%20payments%20won't%20change%20throughout%20the%20life%20of%20the%20loan%20(though%20your%20mortgage%20payment%20could%20increase%20if%20your%20taxes%20or%20insurance%20go%20up).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20exchange%20for%20this%20stability%2C%20you'll%20take%20on%20a%20higher%20rate.%20This%20might%20seem%20like%20a%20bad%20deal%20right%20now%2C%20but%20if%20rates%20increase%20further%20down%20the%20road%2C%20you%20might%20be%20glad%20to%20have%20a%20rate%20locked%20in.%20And%20if%20rates%20trend%20down%2C%20you%20may%20be%20able%20to%20refinance%20to%20snag%20a%20lower%20rate%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20Does%20an%20Adjustable-Rate%20Mortgage%20Work%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fadjustable-rate-mortgage%5C%22%3EAdjustable-rate%20mortgages%3C%2Fa%3E%20start%20with%20an%20introductory%20period%20where%20your%20rate%20will%20remain%20fixed%20for%20a%20certain%20period%20of%20time.%20Once%20that%20period%20is%20up%2C%20it%20will%20begin%20to%20adjust%20periodically%20%E2%80%94%20typically%20once%20per%20year%20or%20once%20every%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20much%20your%20rate%20will%20change%20depends%20on%20the%20index%20that%20the%20ARM%20uses