0and%20long-term%20care.%20I%20also%20work%20with%20family%20members%20of%20the%20deceased%2C%20helping%20them%20navigate%20the%20legal%20processes%20that%20occur%20after%20a%20person%20dies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20person%20dies%2C%20I%20represent%20the%20trustee%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fimportant-things-to-know-as-the-executor-of-an-estate-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexecutor%20of%20their%20estate%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20responsibility%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20follow%20the%20estate%20plan%20that%20the%20person%20who%20died%20created%20or%2C%20if%20the%20person%20didn't%20have%20an%20estate%20plan%2C%20that%20they%20follow%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-happens-if-you-die-without-a-will-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintestacy%20laws%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20will%20dictate%20who%20inherits%20what%20from%20the%20person%20who's%20passed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20in%20this%20line%20of%20work%20since%202012%20when%20I%20joined%20an%20Indiana-based%20law%20firm.%20Around%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20my%20husband%2C%20also%20an%20attorney%2C%20and%20I%20purchased%20the%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I've%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fask-siblings-larger-share-of-inheritance-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edealt%20with%20inheritance%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20my%20job%2C%20I've%20noticed%20that%20putting%20money%20on%20the%20table%20changes%20people.%20I've%20seen%20it%20benefit%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20%E2%80%94%20they%20receive%20money%20or%20property%20they%20didn't%20have%20before%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I'd%20be%20remiss%20if%20I%20didn't%20recognize%20how%20many%20families%20end%20up%20fighting%20over%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22077345e5-aff5-4737-bc8e-d3bbaa456cd7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFamilies%20fight%20over%20property%20that%20is%20valuable%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%20so%20valuable%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20often%20says%20that%20dealing%20with%20estate%20planning%20documents%20is%20the%20easiest%20part%20of%20our%20jobs%20%E2%80%94%20It's%20the%20relationships%20and%20personalities%20involved%20that%20make%20it%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20experience%2C%20it's%20not%20even%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20that%20makes%20families%20fight.%20I've%20seen%20people%20bicker%20over%20personal%20property%20in%20mom%20or%20dad's%20house%20that%20isn't%20worth%20anything%20but%20has%20high%20sentimental%20value%2C%20like%20a%20family%20sword%20or%20jewelry.%20You%20can't%20always%20split%20this%20type%20of%20property%20between%20relatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20once%20tasked%20with%20getting%20a%20valuation%20of%20a%20mother's%20wedding%20ring%20as%20two%20children%20were%20fighting%20over%20it.%20It%20turned%20out%20that%20the%20wedding%20ring%20was%20comprised%20of%20cubic%20zirconia%2C%20not%20real%20diamonds.%20Once%20that%20was%20discovered%2C%20neither%20wanted%20the%20ring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELegal%20fees%20can%20end%20up%20consuming%20estates%2C%20so%20when%20estates%20have%20a%20significant%20amount%20of%20assets%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20more%20time%20and%20room%20for%20families%20to%20argue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20was%20involved%20in%20a%20case%20where%20two%20sisters%20were%20fighting%2C%20and%20their%20legal%20fees%20were%20consuming%20their%20estate%20balance.%20We%20were%20trying%20to%20get%20them%20to%20settle%20their%20dispute%20before%20they%20ran%20out%20of%20money%2C%20but%20one%20of%20the%20siblings%20looked%20us%20dead%20in%20the%20eye%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20rather%20see%20you%20guys%20get%20that%20money%20than%20my%20sister.%26quot%3B%20I%20will%20never%20forget%20the%20look%20on%20her%20face.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20the%20beneficiaries%20walked%20away%20with%20nothing.%20Litigation%20continued%20and%20consumed%20the%20entire%20estate%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%