Heads%20To%20Kanyakumari%20To%20Meditate%2C%20His%2033-Year-Old%20Photo%20Surfaces%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20all%20set%20to%20mark%20the%20end%20of%20a%20hectic%20poll%20campaign%20and%20head%20to%20Kanyakumari%20today%20for%20a%20two-day%20meditation%20at%20the%20iconic%20Vivekananda%20Rock%20Memorial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20PM%20Modi's%20visit%20down%20south%2C%20his%2033-year-old%20pictures%20from%20the%20iconic%20spot%20surfaced%20on%20social%20media%20on%20Thursday%20and%20took%20the%20netizens%20by%20storm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pictures%20dated%20December%2011%2C%201991%2C%20are%20from%20Ekta%20Yatra%20that%20commenced%20from%20the%20iconic%20Vivekananda%20Rock%20Memorial%20in%20Kanyakumari%20and%20ended%20in%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20viral%20pictures%2C%20all%20the%20'Ekta%20Yatris'%20including%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20party%20veteran%20Dr%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%20can%20be%20seen%20at%20the%20statue%20of%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20to%20pay%20their%20respects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20Ekta%20Yatra%2C%20also%20termed%20as%20the%20Unity%20March%20was%20launched%20in%20December%201991%20from%20Kanyakumari%20and%20culminated%20on%20January%2026%2C%201992%2C%20with%20the%20hoisting%20of%20the%20national%20flag%20in%20Srinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ekta%20Yatra%20was%20led%20by%20veteran%20BJP%20leader%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%20while%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20then%20a%20BJP%20worker%2C%20served%20as%20a%20key%20pivot%20in%20organising%20the%20march.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20of%20the%20Yatra%20was%20to%20send%20a%20strong%20message%20to%20the%20world%20that%20India%20would%20stand%20firm%20and%20united%20against%20the%20forces%20of%20terror.%20The%20journey%20spanning%2014%20states%20resonated%20deeply%20with%20the%20people%20and%20showed%20the%20country's%20unwavering%20commitment%20to%20national%20unity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20from%20May%2030-June%201%2C%20PM%20Modi%20is%20set%20to%20undertake%2048-hour%20meditation%20at%20Dhyan%20Mandapam%2C%20the%20spot%20where%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20meditated%20in%201892.%20The%20Rock%20Memorial%20monument%20was%20built%20to%20pay%20tribute%20to%20the%20Hindu%20philosopher-saint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20said%20that%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20after%20wandering%20across%20the%20country%20meditated%20here%20for%20three%20days%20and%20attained%20a%20vision%20for%20a%20developed%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20had%20undertaken%20a%20similar%20spiritual%20journey%20after%20the%20culmination%20of%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20His%20visit%20to%20Uttarakhand%20after%20the%20high-octane%20campaign%20and%20meditation%20inside%20a%20cave%20near%20the%20Kedarnath%20shrine%20drew%20global%20headlines.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717061580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F04cm3gpg_narendra-modi-photo-at-vivekananda-rock-memorial-from-1991_625x300_30_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-pm-narendra-modi-heads-to-kanyakumari-to-meditate-his-33-year-old-photo-surfaces-online-5778255%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20all%20set%20to%20mark%20the%20end%20of%20a%20hectic%20poll%20campaign%20and%20head%20to%20Kanyakumari%20today%20for%20a%20two-day%20meditation%20at%20the%20iconic%20Vivekananda%20Rock%20Memorial.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-pm-narendra-modi-heads-to-kanyakumari-to-meditate-his-33-year-old-photo-surfaces-online-5778255%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-pm-narendra-modi-heads-to-kanyaku