%20has%20plunged%20to%20under%20six%20per%20cent...%20during%20Congress-UPA%20tenure%20it%20was%20about%20eight%20per%20cent%20(New%20Series).%20Unprecedented%20unemployment%20and%20unbridled%20inflation%20have%20greatly%20widened%20inequality%2C%20which%20is%20now%20at%20a%20100-year%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20PM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20World%20Bank%20data%20GDP%20growth%20under%20the%20UPA%20government%20touched%20a%20high%20of%208.5%20per%20cent%20in%202010%2C%20and%20hit%20a%20low%20of%203.1%20per%20cent%20in%202008%20(during%20the%20global%20financial%20crisis).%20In%20the%2010%20years%20since%20it%20has%20reached%20a%20high%20of%209.1%20per%20cent%20(in%202021)%20and%20plummeted%20to%20-5.8%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20Explains%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-black-paper-news-bjp-white-paper-price-rise-unemployment-congress-black-paper-attack-on-government-5019669%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BPrice%20Rise%2C%20Joblessnes...%26quot%3B%3A%20Congress'%20Black%20Paper%20On%20Centre%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20Dr%20Singh's%20letter%20was%20shared%20on%20X%20by%20the%20Congress%20an%20hour%20after%20the%20central%20bank%20released%20its%20annual%20report%2C%20in%20which%20it%20forecast%20real%20GDP%20growth%20of%20seven%20per%20cent%20for%20FY2024%2F25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20a%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20report%20pegged%20overall%20FY2023%2F24%20growth%20at%20eight%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Singh%20said%20the%20UPA%20%26quot%3Bdespite%20challenges%2C%20had%20increased%20purchasing%20power%20of%20our%20people%26quot%3B%2C%20while%20%26quot%3BBJP%20misrule%20has%20resulted%20in%20depletion%20of%20household%20savings%20to%20historic%2047-year%20low%26quot%3B%3B%20in%20FY2022%2F23%20households'%20net%20financial%20savings%20plunged%20to%20a%20five-year%20low%20of%20Rs%2014.2