nt%20(job)%20vacancies%20(and)%20innumerable%20paper%20leaks%20have%20cast%20a%20dark%20shadow%20on%20their%20future%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20committed%20that%2030%20lakh%20vacancies%20would%20be%20systematically%20filed%20according%20to%20a%20job%20calendar...%20half%20of%20those%20jobs%20would%20be%20reserved%20for%20women%2C%20and%20we%20will%20establish%20fast-track%20courts%20for%20(exam)%20paper%20leak%20cases...%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Singh%20said%20in%20his%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20though%2C%20has%20argued%20that%20indicators%20like%20filed%20income%20tax%20returns%20(3.36%20crore%20in%202014%20to%20over%20eight%20crore%20in%202024)%20suggest%20jobs%20are%20being%20generated.%20Mr%20Modi%20has%20also%20pointed%20to%20Employee%20Provident%20Fund%20data%20-%20over%20six%20crore%20new%20subscribers%20in%20seven%20years%20-%20to%20make%20the%20same%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funemployment-rate-declines-to-6-7-percent-in-indias-urban-areas-survey-5672422%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnemployment%20Falls%20To%206.7%20Per%20Cent%20In%20Urban%20Areas%3A%20Survey%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20government%20report%20last%20week%20said%20unemployment%20rate%20for%20people%20over%2015%20(in%20urban%20areas)%20'fell'%20to%206.7%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20January-March%20period%3B%20it%20was%206.8%20per%20cent%20a%20year%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDr%20Singh%20On%20Agniveer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20mounted%20a%20sharp%20attack%20on%20the%20BJP%20over%20the%20contentious%20Agnipath%20military%20recruitment%20scheme%2C%20which%20the%20Congress%20has%20said%20it%20will%20scrap%20if%20it%20wins%20this%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-