ept%20a%20lot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoing%20so%20has%20helped%20them%20cut%20down%20on%20costs%20and%20get%20creative%20with%20the%20renovation%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20couple%20can't%20afford%20new%20kitchen%20cabinets%2C%20so%20they've%20decided%20to%20use%20old%20wooden%20dressers%20that%20were%20already%20in%20the%20house%20for%20kitchen%20storage%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EKnighten%20and%20Cordier%20might%20have%20been%20happy%20in%20the%20US%2C%20but%20she%20has%20no%20doubts%20Italy%20was%20the%20right%20choice.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kristina%20Knighten%20and%20Paul%20Cordier%20holding%20two%20small%20dogs%20and%20glasses%20of%20wine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664fada0a961b37edf398496%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKnighten%20and%20Cordier%20were%20living%20in%20the%20UAE%20when%20they%20stumbled%20upon%20Lago%20Iseo%20during%20a%20summer%20vacation%20in%202018.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Kristina%20Knighten%20and%20Paul%20Cordier%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKnighten%20has%20no%20regrets%20about%20choosing%20their%20slice%20of%20Italian%20paradise%20over%20a%20chance%20to%20move%20back%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20quality%20of%20life%20here%20is%20beyond.%20It's%20incredible%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20Benefits%20they're%20enjoying%20include%20better%20grocery%20produce%2C%20how%20walkable%20everything%20is%2C%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20free%20healthcare%2C%20which%20the%20couple%20can%20enroll%20in%20because%20they%20are%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20game%20changer%20for%20Knighten%2C%20who%20recalled%20experiencing%20an%20ovarian%20cyst%20rupture%20when%20she%20was%20living%20in%20the%20US%20without%20health%20insurance.%20Despite%20having%20two%20jobs%20at%20the%20time%2C%20she%20hesitated%20to%20go%20to%20the%20hospital%20because%20of%20how%20much%20it%20would%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLooking%20back%20at%20it%2C%20I'm%20like%2C%20how%20is%20America%20considered%20the%20developed%20world%3F%26quot%3B%20Knighten%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20great%20deal%20they%20have%20as%20teachers%20in%20Italy%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteacher-salary-pay-penalty-worse-wage-gap-report-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20poorly%20many%20teachers%20are%20paid%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Knighten%20and%20Cordier%20have%20no%20plans%20to%20move%20stateside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Knighten%20wouldn't%20rule%20anything%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFive%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20didn't%20expect%20to%20be%20doing%20this%2C%20and%2010%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20did%20not%20expect%20to%20be%20in%20the%20UAE%20or%20Vietnam%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'd%20100%25%20live%20in%20Chicago%20again.%20But%20I%20just%20don't%20see%20that%20happening%20for%20me%2C%20especially%20in%20my%20profession.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteachers-buy-house-in-italy-instead-of-more-expensive-usa-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717060381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664f9d42239fda2da6cb33ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteachers-buy-house-in-italy-instead-of-more-expensive-usa-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20couple%20planned%20to%20move%20to%20the%20US%20when%20they%20stumbled%20across%20an%20Italian%20lake%20with%20cheaper%20homes%2C%20fresher%20groceries%2C%20and%20better%20healthcare.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mnoyen%40insider.com%20(Maria%20Noyen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A124%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteachers-buy-house-in-italy-instead-of-more-expensive-usa-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl