20been%20battling%20a%20severe%20heatwave%20over%20the%20last%20two%20weeks.%20While%20Mungeshpur%2C%20on%20the%20city's%20northwestern%20fringes%2C%20saw%20the%20mercury%20touching%2052.9%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20a%20person%20died%20in%20a%20city%20hospital%20due%20to%20heatstroke.%20The%20intense%20heat%20has%20sparked%20health%20concerns%2C%20including%20that%20of%20direct%20exposure%20to%20the%20sun's%20rays%2C%20which%20increases%20the%20risk%20of%20an%20eye%20stroke.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20is%20an%20eye%20stroke%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEye%20stroke%20occurs%20from%20a%20lack%20of%20sufficient%20blood%20flow%20to%20the%20tissues%20located%20in%20the%20front%20part%20of%20the%20optic%20nerve%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pennmedicine.org%2Ffor-patients-and-visitors%2Fpatient-information%2Fconditions-treated-a-to-z%2Feye-stroke%23%3A~%3Atext%3DRisk%2520Factors%2520of%2520Eye%2520Stroke%2Crisk%2520for%2520developing%2520the%2520disease.%5C%22%3EPenn%20Medicine%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Also%20called%20anterior%20ischemic%20optic%20neuropathy%2C%20eye%20stroke%20is%20a%20dangerous%20and%20potentially%20debilitating%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20states%20that%20If%20the%20blockage%20occurs%20as%20the%20blood%20vessels%20emerge%20out%20of%20the%20optic%20nerve%20and%20onto%20the%20retina%2C%20it%20is%20called%20a%20central%20or%20branch%20retinal%20artery%20occlusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20eye%20stroke%20can%20cause%20sudden%20loss%20of%20vision%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EImpact%20of%20heat%20on%20eye%20health%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeatwaves%20can%20negatively%20impact%20your%20overall%20eye%20health%20by%20causing%20dehydration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20results%20in%20dry%20eyes%20and%20irritation.%20If%20there%20is%20an%20increase%20in%20exposure%20to%20harmful%20ultraviolet%20(UV)%20rays%2C%20it%20can%20damage%20the%20eyes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20this%20increases%20the%20risk%20of%20conditions%20like%20cataracts%2C%20and%20macular%20degeneration%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20high%20temperatures%20can%20aggravate%20allergies.%20More%20frequent%20eye%20rubbing%20can%20introduce%20infections%20or%20cause%20further%20irritation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3ESymptoms%20of%20eye%20stroke%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pennmedicine.org%2Ffor-patients-and-visitors%2Fpatient-information%2Fconditions-treated-a-to-z%2Feye-stroke%23%3A~%3Atext%3DRisk%2520Factors%2520of%2520Eye%2520Stroke%2Crisk%2520for%2520developing%2520the%2520disease.%5C%22%3Emajor%20symptoms%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20eye%20stroke%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDryness%20in%20eyes%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EConstant%20irritation%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBlurry%20vision%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EConjunctivitis%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESwelling%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESudden%20vision%20loss%20in%20one%20eye%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELoss%20of%20visual%20contrast%20or%20light%20sensitivity%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3ETips%20to%20stay%20safe%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWear%C2%A0sunglasses%20to%20protect%20your%20eyes%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fhealth%2Fkeep-your-eyes-safe-by-following-these-tips-during-heatwaves-5770136%5C%22%3Eharmful%20UV%20rays%20causing%20cataracts%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20macular%20degeneration%2C%20and%20other%20eye%20damage.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStay%20hydrated%20to%20avoid%20health%20issues%20related%20to%20heatwaves.%20Drink%20at%20least%20eight%20glasses%20of%20water%20every%20day%2C%20and%20more%20if%20you%20spend%20time%20in%20the%20heat.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUV-blocking%20contact%20lenses%20provide%20an%20extra%20layer%20of%20protection%20against%20UV%20rays.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEating%20eye-healthy%20food%20with%20nutrients%20like%20omega-3%20fatty%20acids%2C%20vitamins%20C%20and%20E%2C%20and%20zinc%20can%20support%20overall%20eye%20health.%20These%20nutrients%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20eye%20conditions%20exacerbated%20by%20heat%20and%20UV%20exposure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWearing%20a%20hat%20every%20time%20you%20step%20out%20in%20the%20sun%20reduces%20direct%20sunlight%20exposure%20to%20the%20eyes.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717059780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fd0p53lag_heatwave-afp_625x300_30_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-is-eye-stroke-caused-by-extreme-heat-can-it-lead-to-loss-of-vision-5776815%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20has%20been%20battling%20a%20severe%20heatwave%20over%20the%20last%20two%20weeks.%20While%20Mungeshpur%2C%20on%20the%20city's%20northwestern%20fringes%2C%20saw%20the%20mercury%20touching%2052.9%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20a%20person%20died%20in%20a%20city%20hospital%20due%20to%20heatstroke.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-is-eye-stroke-caused-by-extreme-heat-can-it-lead-to-loss-of-vision-5776815%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-is-eye-stroke-caused-by-extreme-heat-can-it-lead-to-loss-of-vision-5776815%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-is-eye-stroke-caused-by-extreme-heat-can-it-lead-to-loss-of-vision-5776815%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20has%20done%20double%20PhD%20in%20corruption%3A%20PM%20Modi%20in%20Punjab%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717059725000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110560102%2Cimgsize-1064647.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Findi-bloc-insulting-spirit-of-constitution-baba-saheb-ambedkar-pm-modi-attacks-opposition-in-punjabs-hoshiarpur%2Farticleshow%2F110560106.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%20criticized%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20in%20a%20rally%20at%20Punjab's%20Hoshiarpur%2C%20emphasizing%20the%20importance%20of%20a%20full%20majority%20government%20for%20continued%20development%20and%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20poor.%20He%20also%20highlighted%20the%20dream%20of%20a%20developed%20India%20and%20the%20upcoming%20polling%20for%20the%2013%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Punjab.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Findi-bloc-insulting-spirit-of-constitution-baba-saheb-ambedkar-pm-modi-attacks-opposition-in-punjabs-hoshiarpur%2Farticleshow%2F110560106.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Army-Cops%20Clash%20In%20J%26amp%3BK's%20Kupwara%2C%20Case%20Against%2016%20Including%203%20Lt%20Colonels%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20police%20have%20filed%20a%20case%20against%2016%20army%20soldiers%2C%20including%20three%20officers%2C%20for%20assaulting%20policemen%20at%20a%20police%20station%20in%20Kupwara%20district.%20Five%20police%20personnel%2C%20including%20the%20Station%20House%20Officer%2C%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20incident%2C%20official%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20purportedly%20showing%20the%20soldiers%20storming%20inside%20the%20police%20station%20late%20Tuesday%20evening%20was%20widely%20shared%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20army%20has%20denied%20assaulting%20the%20cops%20and%20termed%20it%20an%20incident%20of%20%26quot%3Bminor%20differences%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reports%20of%20altercation%20between%20police%20and%20army%20personnel%20and%20beating%20of%20police%20personnel%20are%20mis-founded%20and%20incorrect.%20Minor%20differences%20between%20the%20police%20personnel%20and%20a%20territorial%20army%20unit%20on%20an%20operational%20matter%20have%20been%20amicably%20resolved%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20defence%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20FIR%2C%20police%20have%20named%2016%20soldiers%2C%20including%20three%20officers%20holding%20the%20rank%20of%20Lt%20Colonel.%20They%20have%20been%20booked%20on%20charges%20of%20rioting%2C%20attempt%20to%20murder%2C%20and%20the%20kidnapping%20of%20policemen%20at%20the%20police%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20cops%20raided%20the%20house%20of%20a%20territorial%20army%20soldier%20at%20Batpora%20village%20in%20Kupwara%20as%20part%20of%20their%20probe%20into%20a%20case%2C%20according%20to%20reports.%20Later%20around%209%3A40%20pm%2C%20the%20army%20soldiers%20swooped%20down%20on%20the%20police%20station%20and%20attacked%20them%2C%C2%A0said%20the%20First%20Information%20Report%20(FIR).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20huge%20number%20of%20armed%20and%20uniformed%20personnel%20of%20160%20Territorial%20Army%2C%20led%20by%20the%20three%20officers%2C%20unauthorisedly%20entered%20the%20police%20station%2C%20it%20said.%20The%20FIR%20said%20the%20troops%2C%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20any%20provocation%2C%20severely%20attacked%20the%20staff%20and%20officers%20present%20at%20the%20police%20station%20with%20rifle%20butts%2C%20kicks%20and%20sticks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20information%20was%20immediately%20conveyed%20to%20senior%20police%20officers%20who%20rushed%20to%20the%20police%20station%20to%20rescue%20them.%20Upon%20seeing%20the%20arrival%20of%20police%20units%20and%20senior%20police%20officers%2C%20the%20alleged%20personnel%20and%20officers%20of%20160%20Territorial%20Army%20led%20by%20Lieutenant%20Colonel%20Ankit%20Sood%2C%20Raju%20Chauhan%2C%20and%20Nikhil%20brandished%20their%20weapons%20and%20snatched%20the%20mobile%20phones%20of%20the%20injured%20personnel%20and%20SHO%20PS%20Kupwara%20Inspector%20Mohammad%20Ishaq%2C%26quot%3B%20reads%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20troops%20have%20also%20been%20accused%20of%20kidnapping%20the%20head%20constable.%20%26quot%3BWhile