%20extension%20of%20interim%20bail%20to%20undergo%20medical%20examinations%2C%20including%20a%20PET-CT%20scan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20registry%20said%20that%20the%20top%20court%20had%20already%20reserved%20its%20verdict%20in%20the%20matter%20and%20the%20application%20seeking%20a%207-day%20extension%20has%20no%20relation%20to%20the%20main%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20allowed%20him%20to%20move%20the%20trial%20court%20for%20obtaining%20regular%20bail%2C%20the%20application%20is%20not%20maintainable%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Kejriwal's%20health%20has%20deteriorated%20since%20he%20was%20arrested%20in%20the%20alleged%20Delhi%20excise%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20said%20that%20he%20has%20lost%207%20kg%20in%20weight%20after%20his%20arrest%20and%20his%20Ketone%20levels%20are%20also%20very%20high%20indicating%20a%20serious%20medical%20disorder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20further%20said%20that%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20required%20to%20do%20medical%20tests%20and%20seven%20days%20were%20needed%20for%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20directed%20him%20to%20surrender%20back%20to%20Tihar%20Jail%20on%20June%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20on%20May%2017%20had%20reserved%20its%20verdict%20on%20Chief%20Minister%20Kejriwal's%20petition%20challenging%20his%20arrest%20and%20subsequent%20remand%20by%20the%20federal%20anti-money%20laundering%20agency%20in%20the%20excise%20policy%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20he%20could%20approach%20the%20trial%20court%20for%20a%20grant%20of%20regular%20bail%20notwithstanding%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20top%20court%20reserved%20judgment%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%