t%20one%20of%20the%20most%20intense%20solar%20events%20in%20recent%20years.%20X-class%20solar%20flares%20are%20the%20strongest%2C%20which%20are%20described%20by%20NASA%20as%20%26quot%3Bgiant%20explosions%20on%20the%20sun%20that%20send%20energy%2C%20light%20and%20high%20speed%20particles%20into%20space%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarth%20has%20already%20experienced%20interruption%20in%20shortwave%20radio%20due%20to%20the%20solar%20storm%2C%20but%20thankfully%20coronal%20mass%20ejection%20(CME)%20from%20the%20latest%20eruption%20will%20not%20impact%20our%20planet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20starburst%20caused%20a%20huge%20coronal%20mass%20ejection%20to%20erupt%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20Sun%20facing%20away%20from%20us%2C%20Ryan%20French%2C%20a%20solar%20physicist%20at%20the%20National%20Solar%20Observatory%20in%20Boulder%2C%20Colorado%2C%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20solar%20storm%20travels%20toward%20Earth%20at%20the%20speed%20of%20light%20and%20ionises%20(gives%20an%20electrical%20charge%20to)%20the%20top%20of%20the%20planet's%20atmosphere%20when%20it%20reaches%20us.%20This%20ionisation%20causes%20a%20higher-density%20environment%20for%20the%20high-frequency%20shortwave%20radio%20signals%20to%20navigate%20through%20to%20support%20communication%20over%20long%20distances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20hit%20by%20these%20charged%20particles%2C%20the%20electrons%20collide%20more%20frequently%20with%20the%20radio%20waves%2C%20leading%20to%20signals%20becoming%20degraded%20or%20completely%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20more%20worry%20among%20the%20scientific%20community%20about%20AR3664%2C%20which%20is%20set%20to%20face%20the%20Earth%20again%20around%20June%206.%20The%20eruptions%20at%20that%20time%20could%20generate%20another%20set%20of%20geomagnetic%20storms%20with%20the%20potential%20to%20impact%20the%20Earth%20adversely.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717056240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-08%2Frga9ooeo_solar-flare-sun-nasa-large_625x300_31_August_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fanother-powerful-solar-storm-headed-towards-earth-blackouts-likely-5777860%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Earth%20has%20already%20experienced%20interruption%20in%20shortwave%20radio%20due%20to%20the%20solar%20storm%2C%20but%20thankfully%20coronal%20mass%20ejection%20(CME)%20from%20the%20latest%20eruption%20will%20not%20impact%20our%20planet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fanother-powerful-solar-storm-headed-towards-earth-blackouts-likely-5777860%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fanother-powerful-solar-storm-headed-towards-earth-blackouts-likely-5777860%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fanother-powerful-solar-storm-headed-towards-earth-blackouts-likely-5777860%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pune%20Porsche%20Teen's%20Mother%20Part%20Of%20Family's%20Big%20Cover-Up%20Plan%2C%20Suspect%20Cops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20blood%20sample%20of%20the%20Pune%20teen%2C%20whose%20late-night%20Porsche%20dash%20left%20two%20young%20engineers%20dead%2C%20may%20have%20been%20swapped%20with%20his%20mother's%20sample%20to%20manipulate%20the%20alcohol%20test%20report%20and%20get%20him%20off%20the%20hook.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20chilling%20crash%20revealing%20massive%20irregularities%20in%20the%2017-year-old's%20medical%20examination%20at%20the%20state-run%20Sassoon%20Hospital%2C%20Maharashtra%20Medical%20Education%20had%20appointed%20a%20three-member%20committee%20headed%20by%20Dr%20Pallavi%20Sapale%2C%20dean%20of%20Mumbai-based%20Grants%20Medical%20College%2C%20to%20look%20into%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel's%20report%2C%20police%20sources%20said%2C%20has%20revealed%20that%20blood%20samples%20of%20a%20woman%20and%20two%20elderly%20men%20had%20been%20collected%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20switching%20the%20teen%20accused's%20sample.%20Police%20now%20suspect%20that%20the%20teen's%20mother%20sample%20had%20been%20collected%20as%20part%20of%20this%20plan%2C%20the%20sources%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20now%20plan%20to%20collect%20samples%20of%20some%20suspects%20to%20get%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20this%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%20They%20are%20looking%20for%20the%20teen's%20mother%20after%20they%20did%20not%20find%20her%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teen's%20mother%20had%20earlier%20appeared%20in%20a%20video%20message%20in%20which%20she%20had%20said%20that%20a%20viral%20video%20purportedly%20featuring%20her%20son%20was%20fake.%20She%20had%20also%20appealed%20to%20the%20police%20to%20%26quot%3Bprotect%26quot%3B%20her%20son%20and%20broke%20down%20on%20camera.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20teen%20accused%20is%20at%20an%20observation%20home%2C%20his%20realtor%20father%20and%20grandfather%20have%20been%20arrested.%20The%20family%2C%20it%20is%20alleged%2C%20tried%20to%20pressure%20their%20driver%20into%20taking%20the%20blame%20for%20the%20accident.%20If%20the%20sample%20under%20probe%20is%20found%20to%20be%20his%20mother's%2C%20it%20will%20point%20to%20the%20involvement%20of%20another%20family%20member%20in%20the%20cover-up%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAneesh%20Awadhiya%20and%20Ashwini%20Kostha%2C%2024-year-old%20engineers%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20were%20killed%20when%20a%20speeding%20Porsche%20hit%20their%20bike%20late%20on%20May%2019.%20The%20teen%2C%20alleged%20to%20be%20driving%20the%20car%20drunk%2C%20was%20out%20on%20bail%20within%2015%20hours%20on%20conditions%20widely%20described%20as%20flimsy%20--%20he%20was%20asked%20to%20write%20a%20300-word%20essay%2C%20told%20to%20work%20with%20traffic%20cops%20for%2015%20days%20and%20seek%20treatment%20for%20his%20drinking%20habit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20growing%20outrage%2C%20the%20Juv