Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20May%2027%2C%20the%2060th%20death%20anniversary%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20Delhi's%20traffic%20police%20imposed%20restrictions%20on%20the%20movement%20of%20vehicles%20in%20the%20capital's%20nerve%20centre%2C%20around%20Pragati%20Maidan%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20India%20Gate.%20No%2C%20the%20curbs%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20anniversary%20of%20India's%20first%20Prime%20Minister.%20Planning%20the%20logistics%20for%20the%20swearing-in%20of%20the%20next%20Prime%20Minister%20necessitated%20it.%20The%20ceremony%20itself%20may%20be%20held%20at%20Bharat%20Mandapam%20in%20the%20Pragati%20Maidan%20complex%2C%20which%20had%20hosted%20the%20G20%20summit.%20It's%20one%20of%20the%20four%20venues%20seeing%20logistic%20and%20security%20drills%20-%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan%2C%20Kartavya%20Path%2C%20and%20the%20National%20War%20Memorial%20being%20the%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20War%20Memorial%20has%20a%20massive%20seating%20capacity%2C%20but%20scorching%20heat%20may%20play%20a%20spoiler.%20Bharat%20Mandapam%20has%20adequate%20infrastructure.%20A%20drill%20was%20conducted%20there%20on%20Tuesday%20as%20well.%20A%20formal%20announcement%20of%20the%20venue%20will%20have%20to%20await%20the%20election%20results%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EModi's%20Tribute%20To%20Vivekananda%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20finishing%20his%20hectic%20campaigning%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20May%2030%20will%20go%20to%20the%20Dhyan%20Mandapam%20at%20Kanyakumari's%20Vivekananda%20Rock%20Memorial%20to%20meditate.%20This%20is%20the%20very%20spot%20where%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20meditated%20in%201892%20and%20had%20a%20vision%20of%20Bharat%20Mata%2C%20which%20led%20him%20to%20push%20for%20the%20conception%20of%20a%20developed%20India.%20Vivekananda's%20name%2C%20before%20he%20became%20a%20monk%2C%20was%20Narendra.%20Viksit%20Bharat%202047%20is%20thus%2C%20in%20a%20way%2C%20Modi's%20tribute%20to%20Vivekananda's%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20verdict%20of%20the%2018th%20general%20election%20is%20due%20in%20a%20week%20from%20now.%20The%20ruling%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20and%20the%20aspirant%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%2C%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%20bloc%20have%20begun%20their%20preparations%20for%20its%20aftermath.%20INDIA%20parties%20had%20planned%20a%20meeting%20for%20June%201%20to%20assess%20their%20poll%20prospects%20and%20to%20chalk%20out%20a%20strategy%20ahead%20of%20the%20results.%20The%20meeting%2C%20convened%20by%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20was%20destined%20to%20derail.%20It%20was%20abandoned%20soon%20after%20its%20announcement%2C%20apparently%20because%20it%20was%20scheduled%20without%20consulting%20others.%20It's%20symbolic%20of%20the%20disunity%20among%20the%2026%20parties%20who%20are%20proclaiming%20a%20change%20of%20guard%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20chief%20and%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20said%20she%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20attend%20the%20meeting%20as%20nine%20seats%20in%20West%20Bengal%20will%20go%20to%20polls%20on%20June%201.%20She%20herself%20has%20to%20cast%20her%20vote%20in%20the%20Kolkata%20Dakshin%20constituency.%20Her%20nephew%2C%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%2C%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20TMC%2C%20will%20have%20to%20oversee%20polling%20in%20his%20Diamond%20Harbour%20seat.%20Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20the%20other%20Trinamool%20leader%20part%20of%20INDIA%20discussions%2C%20also%20cannot%20miss%20the%20photo-op%20of%20voting%20in%20Kolkata.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20was%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20Kharge-led%20Congress%20has%20jumped%20the%20gun%20and%20convened%20a%20bloc%20meeting%20only%20to%20reschedule%20it%20later.%20Perhaps%20the%20deadline%20of%20June%202%2C%20the%20day%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20chief%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20interim%20bail%20expires%2C%20weighed%20on%20Kharge's%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPost-Poll%20Strategies%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETop%20NDA%20leaders%20have%20also%20begun%20strategising.%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Rajnath%20Singh%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20Jagat%20Prakash%20Nadda%20met%20on%20Tuesday%20morning%20before%20Modi%20embarked%20on%20a%20campaign%20tour%20to%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Jharkhand.%20His%20roadshow%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20starting%20at%20Netaji%20Subhas%20Chandra%20Bose's%20statue%20and%20culminating%20at%20Vivekananda's%20birthplace%2C%20was%20symbolic%20not%20only%20for%20Bengal%20voters%20but%20also%20for%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20the%202019%20results%2C%20Modi%20had%20meditated%20at%20Kedarnath.%20This%20year's%20Kanyakumari%20trip%20will%20be%20the%20second%20occasion%20when%20Modi%20will%20meditate%20at%20a%20site%20previously%20used%20by%20Vivekananda.%20A%20few%20years%20back%2C%20he%20had%20spent%20a%20night%20at%20the%20Ramakrishna%20Mutt%20in%20Belur%20near%20Kolkata%20and%20used%20the%20monk's%20room%20for%20meditation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20INDIA%20partners%20are%20grappling%2C%20the%20NDA%20leadership%20has%20already%20charted%20its%20roadmap.%20A%20possible%20Modi%203.0%20may%20see%20the%20migration%20of%20state%20leaders%2C%20a%20few%20former%20chief%20ministers%2C%20and%20even%20a%20few%20serving%20governors%2C%20to%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20swearing-in%20of%20a%20third%20Modi-led%20Cabinet%20may%20signal%20a%20total%20departure%20from%20past%20practices%2C%20ushering%20in%20an%20era%20that%20will%20set%20India%20on%20the%20path%20of%20becoming%20'Viksit%20Bharat'.%20After%20Modi%20became%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20the%20city%20of%20Ahmadabad%20and%20Gujarat's%20capital%2C%20Gandhinagar%2C%20underwent%20a%20huge%20makeover.%20The%20same%20has%20been%20the%20case%20with%20New%20Delhi%20since%20Modi%20emerged%20as%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20progressive%20ruler%20leaves%20his%20imprint%20on%20his%20seat%20of%20governance.%20Colonial-era%20Lutyens'%20Delhi%2C%20set%20up%20by%20the%20British%20as%20their%20Imperial%20Capital%20a%20century%20ago%2C%20seems%20to%20be%20waning.%20The%20Eighth%20City%20of%20Delhi%2C%20which%20may%20well%20be%20recorded%20by%20historians%20in%20the%20future%20as%20Modi's%20Delhi%2C%20has%20been%20in%20the%20making%20since%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%20the%20Central%20Vista%20project%2C%20under%20which%20India%20got%20a%20new%20Parliament%20House%2C%20and%20the%20National%20War%20Memorial.%20Raj%20Path%20has%20been%20renamed%20Kartavya%20Path.%20The%20empty%20canopy%20at%20India%20Gate%2C%20which%20till%201967%20had%20been%20occupied%20by%20a%20statue%20of%20King%20George%20V%2C%20now%20has%20a%20glorious%20statue%20of%20Subhas%20Chandra%20Bose.%20For%2046%20years%2C%20successive%20governments%20had%20debated%20who%20ought%20to%20be%20honoured%20under%20the%20iconic%20canopy.%20Modi's%20decision%20to%20install%20Netaji%20ended%20that%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState-of-the-art%2C%20environmentally%20efficient%20buildings%20have%20started%20coming%20up%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20Kartavya%20Path.%20The%20damp%2C%20crumbling%2C%20Second%20World%20War%20vintage%20structures%2C%20which%20house%20a%20number%20of%20offices%20have%20been%20pulled%20down.%20The%20government%20will%20start%20functioning%20from%20swanky%20office%20blocks%20in%20the%20next%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Swearing-In%20Ceremony%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20swearing-in%20of%20the%20interim%20government%20with%20Nehru%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20on%20September%202%2C%201946%2C%20the%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan%20-%20then%20known%20as%20Viceroy's%20House%20-%20was%20the%20designated%20venue%20for%20the%20installation%20of%20new%20Prime%20Ministers.%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20Morarji%20Desai%2C%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20and%20V.P.%20Singh%2C%20all%20took%20their%20oaths%20there.%20The%20break%20from%20tradition%20came%20when%20Chandra%20Shekhar%20was%20sworn%20in%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20on%20November%2010%2C%201990.%20He%20insisted%20on%20moving%20the%20ceremony%20from%20the%20confines%20of%20Durbar%20Hall%20and%20Ashok%20Hall%20to%20the%20forecourt%20of%20the%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan%20so%20as%20to%20let%20in%20a%20larger%20number%20of%20attendees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EP.V.%20Narasimha%20Rao%2C%20H.D.%20Deve%20Gowda%20and%20I.K.%20Gujaral%20preferred%20the%20confines%20of%20the%20ceremonial%20halls.%20On%20May%2016%2C%201996%2C%20when%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20became%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20at%20the%20head%20of%20a%20regime%20that%20lasted%20a%20mere%2013%20days%20but%20heralded%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20as%20India's%20major%20ruling%20party%2C%20he%20followed%20Chandra%20Shekhar's%20style%2C%20and%20his%20swearing-in%20took%20place%20at%20the%20forecourt%20of%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201998%2C%20when%20Vajpayee%20was%20sworn%20in%20a%20second%20time%2C%20he%20preferred%20to%20move%20the%20ceremony%20out%20of%20the%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan%20to%20the%20Central%20Hall%20of%20Parliament%2C%20the%20venue%20of%20the%20adoption%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%20But%2C%20the%20President%2C%20K.R.%20Narayanan%2C%20did%20not%20agree%2C%20and%20thus%2C%20the%20forecourt%20was%20chosen%20once%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManmohan%20Singh's%20two%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20regimes%20also%20preferred%20the%20confines%20of%20the%20ceremonial%20halls.%20In%20contrast%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%202014%20and%202019%20preferred%20the%20forecourt.%20His%20last%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20had%20a%20record%206%2C500%20invitees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20clear%20yet%2C%20but%20in%20case%20this%20year's%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20is%20held%20at%20Bharat%20Mandapam%2C%20the%20Kartavya%20Path%20or%20the%20National%20War%20Memorial%2C%202024%20will%20signal%20a%20strong%20departure%20from%20Lutyens'%20Delhi%2C%20and%20a%20journey%20towards%20a%20'Viksit%20Bharat'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20Editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717050120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fmcg2vvcg_pm-modi_625x300_22_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthis-years-swearing-in-may-be-a-final-goodbye-to-lutyens-delhi-5777132%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20case%20this%20year's%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20is%20held%20at%20Bharat%20Mandapam%2C%20the%20Kartavya%20Path%20or%20the%20National%20War%20Memorial%2C%202024%20will%20signal%20a%20strong%20departure%20from%20Lutyens'%20Delhi%20and%20a%20journey%20towards%20a%20'Viksit%20Bharat'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthis-years-swearing-in-may-be-a-final-goodbye-to-lutyens-delhi-5777132%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Furiosa%20to%20cross%20Rs%2013%20crore%20mark%20in%20week%201%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717048919000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110554237%2Cimgsize-28290.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fbox-office%2Ffuriosa-a-mad-max-saga-box-office-collection-chris-hemsworth-and-anya-taylor-joy-starrer-to-cross-rs-13-crore-mark-in-week-1%2Farticleshow%2F110554277.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110554277.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BFuriosa%3A%20A%20Mad%20Max%20Saga%2C%26quot%3B%20starring%20Chris%20Hemsworth%20and%20Anya%20Taylor-Joy%2C%20earned%20Rs%2