families%20getting%20financial%20independence%20through%20our%20work%2C%20it%20motivates%20me%20to%20work%20further.%20No%20other%20achievement%20could%20give%20us%20the%20contentment%20we%20experience%20through%20this%20work.%20Every%20night%2C%20I%20sleep%20well%20knowing%2080%20families%20are%20sleeping%20peacefully%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20HimFla.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716976330000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-2-1716968175.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D351421%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sandeep%20Pandey%E2%80%99s%20dreams%20of%20opening%20a%20restaurant%20were%20shattered%20by%20the%202013%20Uttarakhand%20floods.%20Later%2C%20with%20his%20childhood%20friends%20Sourabh%20Pant%20and%20Yogendra%20Singh%2C%20he%20founded%20HimFla%2C%20a%20startup%20selling%20Uttarakhand's%20traditional%20%E2%80%98pahadi%E2%80%99%20salt.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F351421%2Fhimfla-himalayan-flavours-pahadi-salt-pisyun-loon-sandeep-pandey-sourabh-pant-yogendra-singh-uttarakhand%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ancient%20Egyptians%20performed%20cancer%20surgery%2C%20'extraordinary'%20new%20evidence%20indicates%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716964860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F05%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-egypt-ancient-skull_6568482.jpg%3F20240529091252%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fancient-egyptians-performed-cancer-surgery-extraordinary-new-evidence-indicates-13144836%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ancient%20Egyptians%20appear%20to%20have%20carried%20out%20surgery%20on%20people%20with%20cancerous%20cells%2C%20a%20study%20has%20found.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%