g%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20has%20helped%20the%20organisation%20in%20several%20unintended%20ways.%20Beyond%20just%20creating%20a%20more%20equitable%20workforce%2C%20having%20PwDs%20at%20the%20workplace%20has%20helped%20us%20relook%20at%20our%20policies%2C%20processes%20and%20infrastructure%20from%20a%20new%20perspective.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20more%20and%20more%20employers%20warm%20up%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20employing%20lawyers%20with%20disabilities%2C%20the%20industry%20is%20also%20moving%20towards%20becoming%20a%20more%20inclusive%20space%20for%20all.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoing%20this%20sentiment%2C%20Amar%20Jain%2C%20a%20visually%20impaired%20lawyer%20and%20accessibility%20professional%2C%20says%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20lawyer%20with%20a%20disability%2C%20we%20face%20enormous%20barriers.%20The%20data%20provided%20by%20clients%20is%20not%20accessible%2C%20the%20physical%20case%20files%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20digital%20copies.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20a%20number%20of%20progressive%20steps%20being%20taken%20by%20the%20judicial%20system.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20recently%20released%20a%20mandate%20to%20provide%20digital%20copies%20of%20case%20files%20to%20lawyers%20with%20disabilities.%20The%20landscape%20is%20changing%2C%20slowly%20but%20surely%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20little%20understanding%20can%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20such%20a%20situation.%20Anchal%20interned%20at%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%E2%80%99s%20chambers%20as%20a%20student.%20She%20remembers%20how%20forthcoming%20they%20were%20with%20respect%20to%20offering%20%E2%80%98Reasonable%20Accommodations%E2%80%99%20to%20help%20her%20work%20better.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20make%20case%20briefs%20with%20page%20number%20references.%20As%20a%20visually-impaired%20person%2C%20it%20is%20sometimes%20difficult%20to%20find%20the%20right%20page%20number%2C%20so%20I%20use%20p